combine in a large bowl 
 
 - 2.5  cups whole milk
 - 8 eggs 
 - 2 tbsp maple syrup
 - 1 tbsp vanilla 

add

 - 1 lbs cubed bread 

stir every minute until liquid is absorbed 
add half the bread to a greased rectangular pan 
top with 

 - 2 cups frozen fruits 

top with rest of bread
cover with plastic wrap 
refrigerate overnight
set oven to 350
bake 45 minutes until centre is 160F

serve with whipped cream or maple syrup 